          </intro>
          <subparagraph>
            <num>•</num>
            <content>
              <p>Impact Assessment for the Windrush Compensation Scheme  <a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/864199/Windrush_compensation_policy_Impact_Assessment.pdf"><u>https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/864199/Windrush_compensation_policy_Impact_Assessment.pdf</u></a></p>
            </content>
          </subparagraph>
