              <p>Managing Public Money</p>
            </intro>
            <subparagraph>
              <content>
                <p><a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/742189/Managing_Public_Money__MPM__with_annexes_2018.pdf"><u>https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/742189/Managing_Public_Money__MPM__with_annexes_2018.pdf</u></a></p>
              </content>
            </subparagraph>
          </subparagraph>
          <subparagraph>
            <num>•</num>
            <intro>
              <p>Windrush Compensation Scheme guidance</p>
            </intro>
            <subparagraph>
              <content>
                <p><a href="http://www.gov.uk/guidance/windrush-compensation-scheme"><u>www.gov.uk/guidance/windrush-compensation-scheme</u></a></p>
              </content>
            </subparagraph>
          </subparagraph>
        </paragraph>
      </section>
